Run web app inside the container (replace xxxx with a unique port):
cd webapp
export FLASK_APP=app
flask run -h 0.0.0.0 -p xxxx

Setup web app outside the container:
cd webapp
virtualenv venv -p $(which python3) 
source ./venv/bin/activate
pip3 install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt

Run web app outside the container on specific port (replace xxxx with port #):
source ./venv/bin/activate
export FLASK_APP=app
flask run -h 0.0.0.0 -p xxxx

Run web app outside the container, no specific port:
source ./venv/bin/activate
export FLASK_APP=app
flask run
